msgid ""
"You can pass Helm configuration options using ``istioctl --set`` by "
"prepending the string ``values.`` to the option name. For example, "
"instead of this Helm command:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/blog/2019/introducing-istio-operator/index.rst:158
msgid "You can use this ``istioctl`` command:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/blog/2019/introducing-istio-operator/index.rst:163
msgid "values.global.mtls.enabled=true"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/blog/2019/introducing-istio-operator/index.rst:165
msgid ""
"You can also set Helm configuration values in an ``IstioControlPlane`` "
"custom resource. See `Customize Istio settings using Helm "
"</docs/setup/install/istioctl/#customize-istio-settings-using-the-helm-"
"api>`_ for details."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/blog/2019/introducing-istio-operator/index.rst:170
msgid ""
"Another feature to help with the transition from Helm is the alpha `{{< "
